\phantomsection\label{index::doc}


Welcome to  \href{http://kucm.ankitgyawali.com}{Checksheet Manager} `s documentation.
Checksheet Manager is a free online checksheet management system for educational instiutions.

The code is open source, and \href{http://github.com/ankitgyawali}{available on github}. Any issues regarding installation or use of checksheet manager can be reported at  the \href{https://github.com/ankitgyawali/checksheet-manager/issues}{issues} page.

The main documentation for checksheet manager is organized into a couple of sections:
